											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="We see the player step up to the window and stare out. The Iron Throne is collapsing, with a deep glow within it. As one of the wings collapses, the entire place explodes. A perfect circle of light engulfs the Throne, with a rumbling, roiling boom. Eventually, it transitions into an orb of water, the explosion's light making it look like shattered glass, that implodes into a cloud of underwater smoke. (look up Underwater Explosions at 120,000fps for visual ref)" />
										</node>
									</children>
								</node>
							</children>
						</node>
